<html>
  <head>
    <meta chraset="UTF-8">
    <style type="text/css">
      .body-email{
        width: 50% !important;
        margin: auto !important;
      }
      .image-class{
        width: 100% !important;
      }
      .body-content{
        width: 85% !important;
        margin: auto !important;
        text-align: center !important;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif !important;
        color: #00609C !important;
      }
      .email-content{
        font-size: 17px !important;
      }
      .email-divider{
        width: 80% !important;
        margin: auto !important;
        color: #CCEBF8 !important;
        border-color: #CCEBF8 !important;
        background-color: #CCEBF8 !important;
      }
      .link-page{
        color: white !important!
      }
      .email-ignore{
        font-size: 14px !important;
      }
      .web-button{
        background-color: #00609C !important;
        color: white !important;
        font-size: 15px !important;
        border-radius: 15px !important;
        padding: 10px !important;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif !important;
      }
    </style>  
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="body-email">
      <div >
        <img src={{base_URL_test}} alt="signature" class="image-class">
      </div>
      <br/>
      <div class="body-content">
        <div class="body-title">
          <span class="email-content">
            <b>Tu crédito ya casi está listo.</b> Tu código de validación es {{code}}.
          </span>
        </div>
        <br/>  
        <div class="email-divider">
          <hr/>
        </div> 
        <br/>

        <div class="email-ignore">
          <u>*Si no hiciste esta solicitud, por favor omite este mensaje.</u>
        </div>
        <br/>
        <div class="footer-confirmation">
          <button class="web-button" background-color= "#00609C" color= "white" font-size= "15px"
                  border-radius= "15px" padding= "10px" font-family="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" 
                  ><a class="link-page" href={{url}}>Ir a la página web</a></button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br/>
      <br/>
      <div >
        <img src={{footer}} alt="footer" class="image-class" >
      </div>

    </div>

  </body>

</html>
